{"type":"section","nativeType":"section","number":"7518","heading":"Micro-grants for food security","label":"7518 Micro-grants for food security","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7518","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/ch102","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs7518","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":["Editorial Notes","References in TextThe Head Start Act, referred to in subsec. (b)(1)(A)(iv)(I), is subchapter B (§ 635 et seq.) of chapter 8 of subtitle A of title VI of , , , which is classified generally to subchapter II (§ 9831 et seq.) of chapter 105 of Title 42, The Public Health and Welfare. For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see Short Title note set out under and Tables.Pub. L. 97–3595 Stat. 499section 9801 of Title 42Aug. 13, 1981The Food Security Act of 1985, referred to in subsec. (e)(4)(D), is , , . Chapter 4 of subtitle D of title XII of the Act is classified generally to part IV (§ 3839aa et seq.) of subchapter IV of chapter 58 of Title 16, Conservation. For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see Short Title of 1985 Amendment note set out under and Tables.Pub. L. 99–19899 Stat. 1354section 1281 of this titleDec. 23, 1985","CodificationSection was enacted as part of the Agriculture Improvement Act of 2018, and not as part of the Emergency Food Assistance Act of 1983 which comprises this chapter.","Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries","Definition of “Secretary”“Secretary” as meaning the Secretary of Agriculture, see , set out as a note under .section 2 of Pub. L. 115–334section 9001 of this title"],"amendments":["References in TextThe Head Start Act, referred to in subsec. (b)(1)(A)(iv)(I), is subchapter B (§ 635 et seq.) of chapter 8 of subtitle A of title VI of , , , which is classified generally to subchapter II (§ 9831 et seq.) of chapter 105 of Title 42, The Public Health and Welfare. For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see Short Title note set out under and Tables.Pub. L. 97–3595 Stat. 499section 9801 of Title 42Aug. 13, 1981The Food Security Act of 1985, referred to in subsec. (e)(4)(D), is , , . Chapter 4 of subtitle D of title XII of the Act is classified generally to part IV (§ 3839aa et seq.) of subchapter IV of chapter 58 of Title 16, Conservation. For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see Short Title of 1985 Amendment note set out under and Tables.Pub. L. 99–19899 Stat. 1354section 1281 of this titleDec. 23, 1985"],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"a","heading":"Purpose","label":"a Purpose","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7518/a","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7518","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs7518%2Fa","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The purpose of this section is to increase the quantity and quality of locally grown food through small-scale gardening, herding, and livestock operations in food insecure communities in areas of the United States that have significant levels of food insecurity and import a significant quantity of food.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"b","heading":"Definitions","label":"b Definitions","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7518/b","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7518","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs7518%2Fb","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":"Eligible entity","label":"1 Eligible entity","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7518/b/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7518/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs7518%2Fb%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7518/b/1/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7518/b/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs7518%2Fb%2F1%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"i","heading":null,"label":"i","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7518/b/1/A/i","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7518/b/1/A","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs7518%2Fb%2F1%2FA%2Fi","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"an individual;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"ii","heading":null,"label":"ii","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7518/b/1/A/ii","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7518/b/1/A","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs7518%2Fb%2F1%2FA%2Fii","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"an Indian tribe or tribal organization, as defined in ;section 5304 of title 25","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"iii","heading":null,"label":"iii","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7518/b/1/A/iii","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7518/b/1/A","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs7518%2Fb%2F1%2FA%2Fiii","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subclause","nativeType":"subclause","number":"I","heading":null,"label":"I","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7518/b/1/A/iii/I","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7518/b/1/A/iii","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs7518%2Fb%2F1%2FA%2Fiii%2FI","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"a religious organization;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subclause","nativeType":"subclause","number":"II","heading":null,"label":"II","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s7518/b/1/A/iii/II","parentIdentifie